## Audit Checklist

### Story 2.1: Display Fleet Summary KPIs
```typescript
// Playwright test:
await page.goto('/');
await expect(page.locator('[data-testid="kpi-total-trains"]')).toBeVisible();
await page.screenshot({ path: 'evidence-2-1-kpis.png' });
```
- [ ] Total Trains KPI visible
- [ ] Available KPI visible
- [ ] In Maintenance KPI visible
- [ ] Km Variance KPI visible
- [ ] Values are numeric (not "undefined" or "NaN")
- [ ] EN 15380 terminology used

### Story 2.2: Show Variance Traffic-Light Indicator
```typescript
// Playwright test:
await page.goto('/');
const variance = page.locator('[data-testid="kpi-variance"]');
await expect(variance).toHaveClass(/green|yellow|red/);
```
- [ ] Traffic light color visible
- [ ] Green when ≤10%
- [ ] Yellow when 10-20%
- [ ] Red when >20%
- [ ] Tooltip shows target

### Story 2.3: Display Depot Capacity Cards
```typescript
// Playwright test:
await page.goto('/');
const cards = page.locator('[data-testid="depot-card"]');
await expect(cards).toHaveCount({ min: 5 });
```
- [ ] Depot cards visible in grid
- [ ] Each card shows depot name
- [ ] Occupancy bar visible
- [ ] Percentage colored appropriately
- [ ] Clicking navigates to depot

### Story 2.4: Show Maintenance Alerts
```typescript
// Playwright test:
await page.goto('/');
await expect(page.locator('[data-testid="maintenance-alerts"]')).toBeVisible();
```
- [ ] Alerts panel visible
- [ ] Count of upcoming events shown
- [ ] List of next 5 events
- [ ] Clicking navigates to Gantt

### Story 2.5: Enable Drill-Down Navigation
```typescript
// Playwright test:
await page.goto('/');
await page.click('[data-testid="kpi-available"]');
await expect(page).toHaveURL(/fleet/);
```
- [ ] Click Available → Fleet (status=fit)
- [ ] Click In Maintenance → Gantt
- [ ] Click Km Variance → Balancing
- [ ] Click Depot Card → Fleet (depot filter)
- [ ] Navigation is smooth (no full reload)

